AI Agent Contract

Primary contract:
  Use Wiki Graph URIs as stable object handles.

Treat every search result as a Wiki Graph URI.

Default exploration loop:
  1. `wikigraph search <archive.sdpub> <query>`
  2. `wikigraph get <archive.sdpub> <uri>`
  3. `wikigraph related <archive.sdpub> <uri>`
  4. `wikigraph evidence <archive.sdpub> <uri>`
  5. `wikigraph pack <archive.sdpub> <uri> --budget <chars>`

Use `--type` on search to filter currently searchable object kinds:
  source, summary, chunk

Use `--json` or `--jsonl` when a stable machine-readable result is needed.
